==French==
===Etymology===
From an earlier ''freid'', [[w:Old French language|Old French]] ''freit'' from [[w:Vulgar Latin|Vulgar Latin]] ''[[frigidus]]'' from the [[w:Latin language|Classical]] ''[[frīgidus]].''

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /fʁwa/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /fRwa/

